            "url": "https://kimgabe.github.io/2021/07/14/02-numpy/",
            "title": "[파이썬 기초] 02. Numpy_random 서브 모듈로 ndarray 데이터 생성하기",
            "date_published": "2021-07-13T15:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Numpy의 random 서브 모듈을 활용해 다양한 ndarray를 만드는 방법을 정리합니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"random-서브모듈-함수를-통해-ndarray-생성하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#random-서브모듈-함수를-통해-ndarray-생성하기\">#</a> random 서브모듈 함수를 통해 ndarray 생성하기</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> numpy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> np</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"random-서브모듈\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#random-서브모듈\">#</a> random 서브모듈</h2>\n<h3 id=\"random-함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#random-함수\">#</a> random 함수</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>0 ~ 1 <strong>보다 작은</strong> 값의 범주에서 랜덤한 ndarray 생성</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>tuple 형식으로 입력해줘야 한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[0.47703558, 0.80144711, 0.74040119],<br />\n[0.31862146, 0.690049  , 0.82771048]])</p>\n<h3 id=\"rand-함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#rand-함수\">#</a> rand 함수</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>0, 1사이의 분포로 랜덤한 ndarray 생성</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 1차원</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rand<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([0.4431507 , 0.46957526])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 2행 3열 의 ndarray생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rand<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[0.70933344, 0.25348086, 0.63018799],<br />\n[0.3784231 , 0.84538854, 0.59128912]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[0.90562321, 0.7034081 , 0.43548124],<br />\n[0.31597773, 0.68466077, 0.68904796]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 5행 3열의 행렬이 4개 생성 ->3차원 ndarray</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rand<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[[0.43037496, 0.45892116, 0.43941642],<br />\n[0.30684635, 0.40820547, 0.32082638],<br />\n[0.7299209 , 0.44457403, 0.76065168],<br />\n[0.71211036, 0.12228115, 0.98060708],<br />\n[0.47309384, 0.55434374, 0.21288774]],</p>\n<pre><code>   [[0.7030427 , 0.24030721, 0.89636842],\n    [0.72449829, 0.94790877, 0.45735653],\n    [0.31077326, 0.49873703, 0.65385706],\n    [0.7214069 , 0.57174121, 0.65875851],\n    [0.87494319, 0.04364989, 0.37346273]],\n\n   [[0.83665403, 0.47537478, 0.24707776],\n    [0.42113453, 0.68517459, 0.77690977],\n    [0.31956091, 0.38027256, 0.57287284],\n    [0.48671635, 0.47045021, 0.89825168],\n    [0.59415424, 0.37183253, 0.6928423 ]],\n\n   [[0.0917947 , 0.24222904, 0.35560574],\n    [0.76962856, 0.17512692, 0.74138208],\n    [0.08833711, 0.28558716, 0.45292481],\n    [0.37076011, 0.14093546, 0.77660625],\n    [0.21051989, 0.36251472, 0.81577139]]])\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"randn함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#randn함수\">#</a> randn함수</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>n: normal distribution(정규분포)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>정규분포로 샘플링된 랜덤 ndarray 생성</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 1차원 벡터 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([-1.51052048, -0.27519631, -0.8666378 , -1.63978589, -0.8215562 ])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 3행 4열 짜리 정규분포에서 sampling한 값 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[-0.72880075, -1.51866859,  1.59485183,  0.12828884],<br />\n[-0.34870788, -0.94093072, -0.65373912, -0.34454653],<br />\n[ 0.34429117, -0.67213369, -0.09330556, -0.19039838]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 4행 2열짜리 행렬을 3개 -> 3차원</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[[-1.37911421,  0.39138757],<br />\n[ 0.72435775, -0.32727131],<br />\n[-1.17817337,  0.70851049],<br />\n[ 0.47210005, -0.17513222]],</p>\n<pre><code>   [[-0.59636136,  0.30423486],\n    [-0.28650705,  0.20916995],\n    [ 1.74434258, -2.11632065],\n    [-0.98421197, -1.38944896]],\n\n   [[ 0.24653031, -1.44258126],\n    [ 0.29318149, -0.2206329 ],\n    [ 0.93137456, -0.87487388],\n    [-0.55208743,  0.37306698]]])\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"randint-함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#randint-함수\">#</a> randint 함수</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>특정 정수 사이에서 랜덤하게 샘플링</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 1부터 100사이의 수에서 5행짜리 1차원 벡터를 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randint<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([35, 58, 84, 11, 11])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 1부터 100사이의 수에서 5행 3열짜리 2차원 벡터를 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randint<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 5, 39, 71],<br />\n[84, 23, 22],<br />\n[99, 37, 47],<br />\n[ 7, 11, 46],<br />\n[42, 26, 44]])</p>\n<h2 id=\"seed-함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#seed-함수\">#</a> seed 함수</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>위에서 실습한 random함수는 실행할때마다 매번 값이 바뀌게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>랜덤한 값을 동일하게 다시 생성하고자 할때 사용</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 0.44477548, -0.37859929, -1.04881793,  1.05633961],<br />\n[ 1.23118506,  0.47478283,  1.72586718, -0.01090185],<br />\n[ 0.35476691, -1.16995451,  0.15202883, -0.27486997]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[-0.3978982 , -1.01173682,  0.40429942, -1.42901326],<br />\n[-0.1511208 ,  0.15430208, -0.32847991, -0.64725463],<br />\n[-1.69742934, -0.16331764,  0.10646885,  1.03418604]])</p>\n<p>동일한 범위지만 호출할때마다 값이 바뀐다.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>seed<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">23</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#seed는 임의의 수 사용</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 0.66698806,  0.02581308, -0.77761941,  0.94863382],<br />\n[ 0.70167179, -1.05108156, -0.36754812, -1.13745969],<br />\n[-1.32214752,  1.77225828, -0.34745899,  0.67014016]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>seed<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">23</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>randn<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[ 0.66698806,  0.02581308, -0.77761941,  0.94863382],<br />\n[ 0.70167179, -1.05108156, -0.36754812, -1.13745969],<br />\n[-1.32214752,  1.77225828, -0.34745899,  0.67014016]])</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>seed를 선정했을 경우 동일 seed일때는 동일한 random값이 출력된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>실험할때나 쉐도잉을 할때 사용하면 유용하다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"choice\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#choice\">#</a> choice</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>주어진 1차원 ndarray로 부터 랜덤으로 샘플링</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>정수가 주어진 경우, np.arange(해당숫자)로 간주</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 1부터 100사이의 수</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 3행 4열 ndarray생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>choice<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[79, 90, 62, 57],<br />\n[19, 33, 59, 39],<br />\n[15, 36, 65,  1]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>array<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2.6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 주어진 x에서 2행 2열 형태로 ndarray 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># replace = True가  default값 -> 중복 추출 허용</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>choice<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[2.6, 1.5],<br />\n[1.5, 2.6]])</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 중복 추출 금지</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>choice<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> replace<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token boolean\">False</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[2.6, 1. ],<br />\n[1.5, 4.9]])</p>\n<h2 id=\"확률분포에-따른-ndarray-생성\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#확률분포에-따른-ndarray-생성\">#</a> 확률분포에 따른 ndarray 생성</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>uniform</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>normal 등등</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"uniform-함수\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#uniform-함수\">#</a> uniform 함수</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># uniform -> low ~ high 사이의 값을 가져 오는 것</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 4행 5열 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>uniform<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[2.74942904, 1.8654592 , 2.75215591, 1.94121243, 1.60485579],<br />\n[2.53464481, 1.02068753, 2.35248663, 1.94336175, 2.26833065],<br />\n[2.84085397, 1.26336399, 2.67879335, 2.40971945, 2.93578399],<br />\n[2.80844986, 1.58561196, 1.29487279, 1.28251   , 2.9085976 ]])</p>\n<h3 id=\"normal\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#normal\">#</a> normal</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>지정한 평균, 표준편차의 정규분포를 따르는 값으로만 ndarray생성</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 평균 0, 표준 편차 1의 정규 분포를 따르는 3*3 ndarray</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>random<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([[-0.49566853, -0.01184144,  0.57898537],<br />\n[-0.66227358,  1.33292115, -0.39404436],<br />\n[-2.50408469, -1.37373969,  1.13563154]])</p>\n",
